{"id":68,"date":"2017-02-10T14:54:44","date_gmt":"2017-02-10T14:54:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=68"},"modified":"2018-09-17T15:06:59","modified_gmt":"2018-09-17T15:06:59","slug":"installing-on-iis-windows-server","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/installing-on-iis-windows-server\/","title":{"rendered":"Installing on IIS &#8211; Windows Server"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \">You will <strong>need mod_rewrite enabled<\/strong> to apply the configs below<\/div>\n<p>Place the<strong> web.config file<\/strong> in the folder where you are trying to install Perfex CRM.<br \/>\nUse the following web.config file to install on IIS server.<strong><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p>\n<pre class=\"lang:xhtml decode:true\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\r\n&lt;configuration&gt;\r\n    &lt;system.webServer&gt;\r\n        &lt;rewrite&gt;\r\n            &lt;rules&gt;\r\n                &lt;rule name=\"Imported Rule 1\" stopProcessing=\"true\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;match url=\"^(.*)$\" ignoreCase=\"false\" \/&gt;\r\n                        &lt;conditions logicalGrouping=\"MatchAll\"&gt;\r\n                            &lt;add input=\"{REQUEST_FILENAME}\" matchType=\"IsDirectory\" negate=\"true\" \/&gt;\r\n                            &lt;add input=\"{REQUEST_FILENAME}\" matchType=\"IsFile\" negate=\"true\" \/&gt;\r\n                        &lt;\/conditions&gt;\r\n                        &lt;action type=\"Rewrite\" url=\"index.php?url={R:1}\" appendQueryString=\"true\" \/&gt;\r\n                &lt;\/rule&gt;\r\n            &lt;\/rules&gt;\r\n        &lt;\/rewrite&gt;\r\n    &lt;\/system.webServer&gt;\r\n&lt;\/configuration&gt;\r\n<\/pre>\n<p>If this web.config doesn&#8217;t work try the following:<\/p>\n<pre class=\"lang:xhtml decode:true \">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\r\n&lt;configuration&gt;\r\n\t&lt;system.webServer&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;asp scriptErrorSentToBrowser=\"true\" \/&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;httpErrors existingResponse=\"PassThrough\" errorMode=\"Detailed\"&gt;&lt;\/httpErrors&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;rewrite&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;rules&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t&lt;rule name=\"Imported Rule 1\" stopProcessing=\"true\"&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t&lt;match url=\"^(.*)$\" ignoreCase=\"false\" \/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t&lt;conditions logicalGrouping=\"MatchAll\"&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t&lt;add input=\"{REQUEST_FILENAME}\" matchType=\"IsDirectory\" negate=\"true\" \/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t&lt;add input=\"{REQUEST_FILENAME}\" matchType=\"IsFile\" negate=\"true\" \/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t&lt;\/conditions&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t&lt;action type=\"Rewrite\" url=\"index.php?url={R:1}\" appendQueryString=\"true\" \/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t&lt;\/rule&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;\/rules&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;\/rewrite&gt;\r\n\t&lt;\/system.webServer&gt;\r\n\t&lt;system.web&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;customErrors mode=\"Off\"\/&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;compilation debug=\"true\"\/&gt;\r\n\t&lt;\/system.web&gt;\r\n&lt;\/configuration&gt;<\/pre>\n<p>If you installed Perfex CRM in a subfolder or in a subdomain and both web.config files above doesn&#8217;t work, please try this web.config file:<\/p>\n<pre class=\"lang:default decode:true\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\r\n&lt;configuration&gt;\r\n  &lt;system.webServer&gt;\r\n    &lt;rewrite&gt;\r\n      &lt;rules&gt;\r\n\t  \t\t&lt;clear \/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;rule name=\"MainFolder\" patternSyntax=\"Wildcard\"&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t&lt;match url=\"*\"\/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t&lt;conditions&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t&lt;add input=\"{REQUEST_FILENAME}\" matchType=\"IsFile\" negate=\"true\"\/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t&lt;add input=\"{REQUEST_FILENAME}\" matchType=\"IsDirectory\" negate=\"true\"\/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t&lt;\/conditions&gt;\r\n\t\t\t\t&lt;action type=\"Rewrite\" url=\"index.php\"\/&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;\/rule&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;\/rules&gt;\r\n    &lt;\/rewrite&gt;\r\n  &lt;\/system.webServer&gt;\r\n&lt;\/configuration&gt;<\/pre>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Place the web.config file in the folder where you are trying to install Perfex CRM. Use the following web.config file to install on IIS server. &lt;?xml version=&#8221;1.0&#8243; encoding=&#8221;UTF-8&#8243;?&gt; &lt;configuration&gt; &lt;system.webServer&gt; &lt;rewrite&gt; &lt;rules&gt; &lt;rule name=&#8221;Imported Rule 1&#8243; stopProcessing=&#8221;true&#8221;&gt; &lt;match url=&#8221;^(.*)$&#8221; ignoreCase=&#8221;false&#8221; \/&gt; &lt;conditions logicalGrouping=&#8221;MatchAll&#8221;&gt; &lt;add input=&#8221;{REQUEST_FILENAME}&#8221; matchType=&#8221;IsDirectory&#8221; negate=&#8221;true&#8221; \/&gt; &lt;add input=&#8221;{REQUEST_FILENAME}&#8221; matchType=&#8221;IsFile&#8221; negate=&#8221;true&#8221; \/&gt; &lt;\/conditions&gt; &lt;action [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[26,29],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-68","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-general-informations","category-installation"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/68","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=68"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/68\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=68"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=68"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/